name: Army Shirt
description: 100% Green Cotton. Two Button Closure Flap Chest Pockets. Made in Japan.

name: Navy Independence Hat
description: Made of wool broadcloth. Soft crown with goat hair buckram. Green satin undervisor and inner taping. Authentic felt lettering. Adjustable Leather Strap. Nickel clip. Exclusive for Independence. Made in Seattle.

name: Popover Shirt
description: 100% Cotton. Button-Down Collar. Locker Loop. V-Stitch Chest Pocket. Box Pleat Back. Made in Ashland.

name: Ecrue Warm Up Fleece
description: 100% Polyester Fleece. 1 Button Chest Pocket. Two Way Zipper. Elastic Waist. Elastic Cuff. Made in New York.

name: Mildblend Supply Co. X Momotaro 14.7 with Arc in Indigo
description: 14.7oz Zimbabwe Cotton. Tight Tapered. Horween Shell Cordovan Patch. All Copper fittings. 34 Inch Inseam. Made in Japan. Recommend purchasing one size up.

name: Rogue Territory Supply Jacket Dark Indigo
description: Modern interpretation of the classic denim jacket. 4 pockets clean finished with white bias tape. Placket and interior pocket cut on selvedge. Front welt pockets. Chain-stitched seams. Adjustable tabs on waistband. Raw nickel crossed feather branded buttons. Hand silk screened care instructions on interior. Handmade in downtown Los Angeles.

name: Stevenson Overalls Slinger Jacket in Navy Canvas
description: The Slinger is a ranch jacket designed by Stevenson Overall Co. The front body features V-shaped pleats on both sides and rivets for a distinctive design. Positioning of the top button is low, allowing the collar to open and structure into a horizontal collar. The front yoke is sewn diagonally using flat felled stitching with 5.6mm twin-needle head and all lock stitching is done with a narrow width for a clean finish. Pocket flaps feature a curved stitch design. Backside features vertical pleats with a large buckle-back and each end is inserted between the pleats and sewn. Made in Japan.

name: "3 Tabs For Breakfast" Heavy Winter Flannel - Navy/Salmon
description: From Flat Head's new Winter line. Made of a heavy cotton flannel but the interior has been combed to a super soft feel. The fabric is woven on a vintage loom and therefore has a very three dimensional pattern due to the loom and also the extra heavy gauge of thread. 100% Cotton Selvedge Flannel. Flat Felled Inner Seams. Urea Buttons. Made in Japan. Combed Interior. Rinsed (Will not shrink).

name: Heavy Loopwheeled Zip Hoodie - Black
description: The ultimate loopwheeled hoodie comes from Strike Gold. Their first attempt at doing a loopwheeled hoodie and they win on every count. Available in three colors these heavy weight inner brushed hoodies will last a lifetime and are super soft on the inside and sturdy on the outside. They've been woven a bit tighter than traditional loopwheeled hoodie fabrics to make them a bit more windproof.

name: Nep Denim Jeans - Slim Straight
description: A newly developed denim from Studio D'Artisan using mixed cotton fibers to create a nep denim that has a lot of character even in its raw state. Great details such as a triple stitched yoke and raised and tucked belt loops. 15oz Unsanforized Japanese Selvedge Denim. Indigo-Dyed. Jacquard Loom Woven Pocket Bags. Button Fly. Made in Japan.

name: Stadium Jacket - Black
description: 8oz 100% Cotton Waxed Canvas. Heavy Black Varsity Jacket Ribbing. Quilted Jersey Lining. Gunmetal Double YKK Zipper. Hidden Inner Pocket. Made In USA.
